content: This game is fun and it could be even better with more options to vary up the gameplay.

The game is great for what it is. definitely worth the money spent on it. I only have a few complaints                       1) I was expecting there to be a tron lightcycle style mode. basically 1-8 lines, and the lines continually stretch. they never disappear. Anyone who has seen a tron movie or played armagetron advanced knows exactly what I am talking about                         2) A demo would be nice. I'm glad I did decide to buy it, but the decision would have been easier if I had gotten to play a timed game (maybe like 1-5 minutes) in the survival game mode beforehand.     otherwise, the game is great, fun, and worth every penny.

There are no cardboard box-based stealth sections to this game.  However, it is one of the most entertaining snake/light-cycle games, with plenty of modes to keep you occupied.  Works exceptionally well on both small and big screens, with three different control mechanisms to ensure that you're doing what you mean to be doing.  Simple enough that my three year-old can play it, fleshed out enough so that an adult can play, and play, and play again (and enjoy the very funny comments).  Get it.
Excellent game. It will make you laugh.  This is the most fun Snake game I've ever played.  Very cleaver design.
Extremely addictive for short bursts of fun. UI is extremely nice and many different game modes offer loads of variety.
This game will be staying on my phone.
Do I need to put it any better? Excellent controls and fantastic Snake-meets-Tron-meets-Pac-Man gameplay. BUY IT!
This is awesome the swipe controls are great and everything is smooth and slick.
